(1, 'Akin Skin Care', '<p>Akin Skin Care is blended in the pristine bushland near beautiful Sydney, Australia, Akin Skin Care is a collection of naturally inspired hair, skin and body care products.&nbsp; All Akin Skin Care products are formulated free from: * parabens * mineral oils * silicones * sulfates * synthetic fragrances * artificial colours * petrochemical cleansers * propylene glycol * phthalates * DEA (MEA, TEA) * ethoxylates</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/1.jpg', '2010-04-30 01:30:00', 4473, 0, 0),
(10, 'Mediherb', '<p><strong>Mediherb</strong> :: As the largest purchaser and processing plant of herbs in Australia, MediHerb have actively supported Australian and New Zealand herb growers since the beginning. It is a priority to source herbs from local growers as much as possible and assist with technical support on how best to grow herbs. By working with herb growers in this way, MediHerb have been able to increase the level of knowledge and awareness of issues affecting herb quality.</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/10.jpg', '2010-05-12 01:30:00', 15449, 0, 1),
(11, 'HookTURN BYO Coffee Cup', '<p>Hookturn Industries are the creators of the reusable BYO coffee cup, saving the planet one coffee at a time.</p>\n<p>Made from silicone, it&rsquo;s firm but flexible, light-weight but tough, and  will withstand 200&ordm;C heat. It&rsquo;s pretty much indestructible. Which means  it won&rsquo;t contribute to the mountain of discarded disposable coffee cups  shoved into landfill, that will never decompose because of their polymer  lining.</p>', 'HookTURN ', 0, 'images2/brands/11.jpg', '2010-05-12 01:30:00', 3937, 0, 0),
(4, 'AUM: Organic Skin Care', '<p><strong>AUM: Organic Skin Care</strong></p>\n<p>Every product in the AUM skincare range is certified by either Ecocert or the Australian Certified Organic Agency. This Certification guarantees that every AUM product is formulated using optimum levels of only 100% approved natural and organic ingredients, with 0% petrochemicals or mineral oils. It tells our clients that every step of Aum''s production; from growth, harvest and right through the manufacturing process, is undertaken with genuine environmental respect.</p>', 'IPDC', 0, 'images2/brands/4.jpg', '2010-04-30 01:30:00', 4579, 0, 0),
(17, 'Blooms Health', '<p>Blooms health is one of the oldest fully Australian owned and operated companies, that has been in the business of caring for and supporting the health and well being of consumers since 1936. Since those early days Blooms has continued to focus on the health and well being of you, our consumer. By ensuring our products are backed by proven clinical research and scientific validation you can be assured of getting the best.</p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/17.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 4237, 0, 0),
(14, 'Billie Goat Soap', '<p><strong>Billie Goat Soap</strong> :: We are a boutique soap company nestled in the Ourimbah valley on the Central Coast of New South Wales, Australia. Our soap is made from a combination of luxury oils and fresh goat''s milk (not powdered), and is so gentle it is popular with people who have sensitive skin, eczema or psoriasis.</p>', 'Unique', 0, 'images2/brands/14.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3977, 0, 0),
(15, 'BioCeuticals', '<p>BioCeuticals is Australia&rsquo;s leading provider of nutritional and  therapeutic supplements. BioCeuticals  aims to consistently raise the standards of natural-based therapies. With quality, innovation and integrity as guiding principles,  BioCeuticals is at the forefront of ensuring complementary and  alternative medicines (CAMs) become an integral part of the Australian  allied healthcare industry.</p>\n<p>BioCeuticals has a strong commitment to research, functional formulas  and reliable practitioner support. Our supplements are recognised by  qualified healthcare practitioners as well as patients; a fact that  reflects our reputation as a progressive force in integrative health.</p>', 'BioCeuticals', 0, 'images2/brands/15.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 59329, 0, 1),
(16, 'Bio-Oil', '<p><strong>Bio Oil</strong></p>\n<p>Bio-Oil&reg; is a specialist skincare product that helps improve the appearance of scars, stretch marks and uneven skin tone. Its advanced formulation, which contains the breakthrough ingredient PurCellin Oil&trade;, also makes it highly effective for numerous other skin concerns, including aging skin and dehydrated skin.</p>', 'Dave', 0, 'images2/brands/16.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 4189, 0, 0),
(19, 'Cheeki Water Bottles', '<p><strong>Cheeki Water Bottles</strong></p>\n<p>Cheeki is a fresh new Australian-owned brand that was launched with     the aim of supplying safe, healthy and fun stainless steel bottles. As a     result we hope to encourage a significantly reduced consumption of     disposable plastic water bottles.</p>\n<p><strong><strong><strong><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 16pt;">:: FAST WORLDWIDE DELIVERY  ::</span></strong></strong></strong></p>', 'Cheeki', 0, 'images2/brands/19.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 22795, 0, 0),
(133, 'MD Nutritionals', '<p>MD Nutritionals Practitioner Only was founded with the aim of providing health practitioners with innovative and superior quality nutritional supplements. You will discover the MD Nutritionals products are based on the latest scientific evidence to uphold clinical results.</p>', 'MD Nutritionals', 0, 'images2/brands/133.jpg', '2011-08-13 18:16:34', 3582, 0, 1),
(134, 'Enzo Professional', '<h4 class="title">ENZO Professional is not available for sale online.</h4>\n<h4 class="title"></h4>\n<p>PLEASE VIEW THE <strong>NUTRALIFE ENZOGENOL CAPSULES </strong>HERE:<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.australianvitamins.com/products/view/1765" target="_blank">Nutralife Enzogenol 50mg Capsules</a></strong></p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/134.jpg', '2011-08-15 18:42:38', 3626, 0, 0),
(136, 'Pana Chocolate :: The Conscious Chocolatier', '<p><strong>Pana Chocolate :: Handmade :: The Conscious Chocolatier<br /></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: small;">Handmade. Raw. Vegan. NO Dairy. NO Soy. Gluten Free</span><br /></strong></p>\n<p>We are proud of our Pana chocolate and want everybody to be able to eat   it, so we made sure they  			could. Our chocolate is low GI, vegan and   gluten free and has no dairy or soy.</p>\n<p>Because we use all natural ingredients, no preservatives and a low GI   natural sweetener, our  			chocolate is good for everybody - even   children.</p>\n<p>Our mandate is that everyone, regardless of  dietary requirements, can enjoy  					the variety of chocolate we make.</p>', 'Conscious ', 0, 'images2/brands/136.jpg', '2011-08-25 02:03:45', 6473, 0, 0),
(137, 'Nut Milk Bag', '<p><strong>Nut Milk Bag</strong></p>\n<p>Haven''t heard of a Nut Milk Bag?<br /> It is a <strong>handy tool</strong> that helps you <strong>make fresh, living </strong>and <strong>nutritious milk from a variety of nuts </strong>and <strong>seeds</strong>.&nbsp;  You can also use it to make juice from fresh ingredients, by blending  and then straining the juice through the bag.&nbsp; Yet another use is to  grow sprouts in it.</p>', 'Little Earth', 0, '', '2011-08-31 03:26:18', 4154, 0, 0),
(138, 'Jack N'' Jill', '<p>Jack and Jill natural kids toothpaste has now been re-formulated to be 100% safe for young children &ndash; especially because they have a tendency to swallow it!</p>\n<p>All Jack and Jill natural kids toothpaste packaging is designed to be appealing to children and is cute enough that parents won''t mind them sitting on their bathroom vanity. Alongside the toothpaste we have designed and manufactured the first children&rsquo;s toothbrushes that are made of cornstarch, and are therefore biodegradable and recyclable.</p>\n<p>Did we mention ''cute''?</p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/138.jpg', '2011-09-02 01:14:52', 3511, 0, 0),
(140, 'salus. spa skincare', '<p>salus. spa skincare :: Our high performance formulations are therapeutically active. They  contain powerful botanicals that work to reduce premature aging, natural  plant extracts that assist with increasing hydration and pure essential  oils that create the optimum in health and wellbeing.</p>\n<p>All of our products are formulated with ingredients that protect the  skin and are 100% free from synthetic fragrance and colour, sodium  laurel sulfates, parabens and mineral oils.</p>', 'salus', 0, 'images2/brands/140.jpg', '2011-10-17 22:18:52', 3383, 0, 0),
(141, 'Haines Manuka Honey', '<p><strong>Haines Manuka Honey</strong></p>\n<p>Our New Zealand honeys are unique and our climate and long isolation  from the rest of the world combined with the pure and un-polluted  environment and natural diversity of floral and native NZ trees, ensure a  quality honey unsurpassed from the rest of the world.</p>\n<p><span class="Copy">UMF<strong>&reg;</strong> Manuka honey can be used on application on the skin or consumed. <br /> Its anti-bacterial activity (highly effective at killing bacteria) has  an equivalent concentration to phenol, a common antiseptic. It supports  the natural healing of wounds, burns, digestive tract and throat. The  active ingredients and anti-oxidents in Haines UMF<strong>&reg;</strong> Manuka honey can also be used for added vitality, oral health, active immunity or overall health and wellbeing.</span></p>', 'Leatherwood Int', 0, 'images2/brands/141.jpg', '2011-10-27 21:34:24', 3827, 0, 0),
(142, 'LifeSprings Minerals 75', '<p>LifeSprings have always guaranteed the purity and high quality of their products. There are no preservatives, synthetic substances or flavourings added         that might contaminate the pure and precious final product.There are over 70 different <strong>PLANT DERIVED  MINERALS</strong> in the LifeSprings&trade; Minerals 75 product.</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/142.jpg', '2011-11-06 23:26:24', 3095, 0, 0),
(143, 'Optimal Rx', '<p><span id="content">Optimal Rx is no longer available for sale online<br /></span></p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/143.jpg', '2011-11-09 23:43:43', 3227, 0, 0),
(174, 'ProPlenish', '<p>ProPlenish Marine Collagen restores your body with the nutrients it needs for a glowing complexion and a younger looking you.</p>\n<p>The ProPlenish team is comprised of scientists, researchers, nutritionists and collagen experts.</p>\n<p class="dark_grey">ProPlenish understand and have learnt the delicacy of the human body &ndash; dedicating research to testing, observing and optimising health and well-being, through the help of natural beauty enhancing supplements. Inside and out, they know what works.</p>\n<p class="dark_grey">Based in Melbourne, it&rsquo;s a highly innovative Australian brand and has been recognised as such &ndash; becoming one of the fastest growing health food supplement and beauty companies in the world.</p>', 'Proplenish', 0, 'images2/brands/174.jpg', '2012-10-09 19:00:18', 3960, 0, 0),
(144, 'Ere Perez Natural Cosmetics', '<p><strong>Ere Perez Natural Cosmetics</strong> is an Australian owned company. Ere Perez Natural Cosmetics pride themselves in supplying healthy natural make up that suits every skin type. Ere Perez Natural Cosmetics carefully select our ingredients such as oils, plant extracts and minerals and blend them with antioxidants to create a gentle, highly effective, quick and easy natural make up solution.<br /><br /><strong>Our Commitments</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>We select our natural ingredients with the greatest respect for mankind and the environment.</li>\n<li>We never test our products on animals</li>\n<li>None of our products are manufactured using child labour.</li>\n<li>Our products are full of natural properties that protect your skin''s beauty.</li>\n<li>All our natural products are made and delivered directly to your store.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Ere Perez', 0, 'images2/brands/144.jpg', '2011-11-29 21:18:41', 4179, 0, 0),
(21, 'Denmar Colon Cleanse', '<p><strong>Denmar Colon Cleanse</strong> :: The creator of Colon Cleanse, one of the best and safest intestinal cleansers.</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/21.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 4663, 0, 0),
(23, 'Dr Wheatgrass :: Wheatgrass Healing', '<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Dr Wheatgrass</strong> :: In 1995, Dr. Chris Reynolds (Dr Wheatgrass founder), a general practitioner in Melbourne, Australia, discovered that an extract of wheatgrass had quite extraordinary healing powers in a number of medical conditions such as burns, wound healing, fractures and numerous skin conditions such as steroid-dependent eczema and molluscum contagiosum. </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">He also noted many of his patients gained considerably more energy and stamina, and felt generally much better in themselves after drinking a diluted form of the extract.</span></p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/23.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 18873, 0, 0),
(24, 'Emu Spirit Emu Oil', '<p><strong>Emu Spirit Emu Oil</strong></p>\n<p>Emu Spirit is an all Australian company that was established in 1993. As a small but dedicated team we strive to offer natural products for inflammatory conditions with our Emu Spirit therapeutic and skincare range.</p>\n<p>In 2002 we were the first to successfully list Emu Oil on the Australian Register of Therapeutic Goods (ARTG) as an active ingredient for the treatment of a range of inflammatory conditions.</p>', 'Emu Spirit', 0, 'images2/brands/24.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 4550, 0, 0),
(25, 'Eyre BioBotanics', '<p><strong>Eyre BioBotanics</strong> :: Skin is Natural. So is Eyre.<br /> <br /> Eyre BioBotanics use only Certified Organic, Biodynamic and Wild Harvest BioBotanic Actives. These ingredients are delivered as nature intended. Pure and potent, free of harmful chemicals and genetic modification and absolutely</p>', 'Eyre', 0, 'images2/brands/25.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 4419, 0, 0),
(26, 'Fab Health', '<p>FABHealth products are created for caring health conscious women, men and their families, who want to optimise their health and wellbeing through appropriate dietary supplements.</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/26.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3584, 0, 0),
(27, 'Flordis Natural Medicines', '<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Flordis</strong> is an Australian company solely dedicated to bringing practitioners the very best natural medicines from around the world. </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">Our team of practitioners and professionals shares a wealth of experience both in the herbal medicine and pharmaceutical industries in Australia and abroad, as well as in research, marketing and education.</span></p>', 'Flordis', 0, 'images2/brands/27.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 16041, 0, 0),
(28, 'Grants of Australia', '<p>Grants of Australia, established in 1984 is a proudly Australian, family owned and operated business, producing natural products for your family''s well being. The range includes natural toothpaste and mouthwash, liquid chlorophyll, liquid vitamin B and crystal deodorants.</p>', 'IPDC', 0, 'images2/brands/28.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3940, 0, 0),
(87, 'Nutri -Tech Solutions', '<p>Nutri-Tech Solutions Pty Ltd was established in June, 1994, with the goal  				of improving nutrition from the soil up. Nutri-Tech remain passionately committed to the concept of improving the  				nutrient density of food while reducing the immune assault  				associated with farm chemicals.</p>', 'Unique', 0, 'images2/brands/87.jpg', '2010-07-26 14:36:00', 3979, 0, 0),
(88, 'Neem Health', '<p>Neeming Australia was formed in 1998 when foudners Brian &amp; Carol Williams came to the Gold Coast, Queensland, Australia to live. Neem Health produce and manufacture Neem Rich based products from the Neem Tree which we send all over the world. Neem is well known to contain many healing and insect repellant qualities.</p>\n<p><span style="color: #808000;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: #808000;"><br /></span></span></span></p>', 'Unique', 0, '', '2010-07-26 14:45:48', 3649, 0, 0),
(85, 'Health Kultcha', '<p>Health Kultcha was established to satisfy the growing need for quality information and superior naturopathically formulated products. All ingredients used in their products are either certified organic or of the highest quality available.</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/85.jpg', '2010-07-12 17:20:21', 3599, 0, 0),
(32, 'INDAH Organics Body Care', '<p>INDAH  RAW Body Care is in its raw form. Nourishing, invigorating and  rehydrating the  skin and senses.</p>\n<p>Australian entrepreneur Teisha Lowry, the brains and natural beauty  behind "INDAH, is part of a small minority in the beauty industry working  actively to create honest products with the best constitution of pure  ingredients.</p>\n<p>Designed by Teisha herself, INDAH products use only organic  ingredients such as virgin coconut oil, herbs, spices, fruits and  flowers. The brand is not just about the products; it&rsquo;s about enhancing  the natural radiance of all mind-body types, through education and  nurturing the truth in beauty. Teisha&rsquo;s natural and organic approach towards the  wellbeing of mind and body are reflected in the full range of INDAH  beauty products.</p>\n<p>Free from all chemical  processing, preservatives and artificial  fragrances and unlike mineral  oil based products, hasn''t any adverse side  effects. Handmade using  herbs, spices, fruits and flowers, all picked fresh  from sustainable  fair-trade farms. Passionately created by  Australian Master  Aromatherapist, Teisha Lowry.</p>', 'INDAH', 0, 'images2/brands/32.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 8539, 0, 0),
(34, 'Inika Mineral Cosmetics', '<p><strong>Inika Mineral Cosmetics :: </strong>Inika is an all Australian natural  cosmetic company which uses quality minerals sourced from the very rocks  that form our land. Inika was founded by business partners Miranda Bond  and Jenni Williams. When Miranda and Jenni were searching for a natural  cosmetic line, they firstly could not find an all-natural Australian  make up company. When they did find so called &ldquo;natural&rdquo; cosmetic lines  overseas they found that many which promote themselves as ''natural'' were  including chemical ingredients or bismuth oxychloride, parabens, or  talc.</p>', 'Inika', 0, 'images2/brands/34.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 16597, 0, 0),
(35, 'Jurlique Skin Care', '<p><strong>Jurlique Skin Care</strong></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">FINAL DAYS!</span></strong></span><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;"> Due to changes in Jurlique''s company structure, we will no longer be stocking Jurlique skincare after August 2014. Jurlique Skincare products will be available in the Jurlique retail stores. </span><br /></strong></p>\n<p>Jurlique source the purest and most innovative ingredients from around the world. The resulting blends harness the living energy of plants and translate that energy into luxurious, vital products that foster timeless radiance and natural good health.<br /> <br /> We nurture our biodynamically grown plants and herbs with great care and integrity at our farm in South Australia.</p>', 'Jurlique', 0, 'images2/brands/35.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 5871, 0, 0),
(36, 'Lalisse Skin Solutions', '<p>Lalisse Skin Solutions offers quick and effective results for problem skin. A natural skin care system that works. Bringing together knowledge from ancient remedies and the expertise of the present.</p>\n<p>The Lalisse product ranges take advantage of the most valuable skin  care properties from natural and herbal ingredients to tackle skin  problems such as acne, dry skin and oily skin.</p>\n<p>Lalisse uses the latest technology to extract these natural ingredients and deliver skin care solutions that actually work.</p>', 'Lalisse ', 0, 'images2/brands/36.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 6157, 0, 0),
(37, 'Lifestream', '<p><strong>Lifestream</strong> :: In line with our reputation, we at Lifestream are very meticulous about the quality of the materials used in our products. Our chosen ingredients and raw materials come only from highly reputable suppliers, are fully tested and guaranteed and are certified organic wherever possible.</p>', 'Planet Health', 0, 'images2/brands/37.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 4754, 0, 0),
(38, 'Vital Greens :: Vital Protein', '<p><strong>Vital Greens :: Vital Protein </strong>:: Vital Greens was developed over 11 years ago by two iconic Sydney naturopaths, Shane Sullivan and Stephen Sprada.</p>\n<p>A decade ago, Shane and Stephen noticed an influx of people with gut,  bowel and digestive problems. Many of their clients were taking large  amounts of supplements, some up to 30 tablets a day.</p>\n<p>Shane and Stephen therefore created a comprehensive powder formula that addressed digestive conditions and poor absorption.</p>\n<p>Vital Protein (formerly Phyto-protein) is the highest concentration  of vegetable plant protein available, and an ideal companion to Vital  Greens. Because it is a vegetable based complete protein, it is suitable  for those who suffer from allergies and have restricted diets.</p>', 'Martin & Pleasance', 0, 'images2/brands/38.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 10412, 0, 0),
(39, 'Loving Earth Superfoods', '<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><strong>Loving Earth Superfoods</strong></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><strong>Quick Links:</strong> <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/1317">Bee Pollen</a> :: <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/885">Maca Powder</a> :: <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/881">Goji Berries</a> :: <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/887">Cacao Butter</a> :: <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/889">Cacao Nibs</a> :: <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/888">Cacao Powder</a> :: <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/893">Camu Camu</a> :: <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/895">Purple Corn Extract</a> :: <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/891">Yacon Syrup</a> :: <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/886">Nopal Powder</a> :: <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/1445">Drinking Chocolate</a> ::   <span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Cambria;" lang="EN-US"><a href="../../../products/view/894">Coconut Oil</a></span> <!-- @font-face {   font-family: "&#65325;&#65331; &#26126;&#26397;"; }@font-face {   font-family: "Cambria Math"; }@font-face {   font-family: "Cambria"; }p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal { margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Cambria; }a:link, span.MsoHyperlink { color: blue; text-decoration: underline; }a:visited, span.MsoHyperlinkFollowed { color: purple; text-decoration: underline; }.MsoChpDefault { font-family: Cambria; }div.WordSection1 { page: WordSecti --><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Cambria;" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;">Loving  Earth source the highest quality organic and wildcrafted ancient   superfoods from around the world. They contain the optimal levels of   phytonutrients, vitamins and minerals.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;">A key part of our mission at Loving Earth is to source products from the  Indigenous communities where they originated. This supports these  unique and special indigenous communities in maintaining their cultural  integrity. Most of the functional foods that we source have played a  central role in the cultural heritage of the indigenous communities that  have cultivated and/or harvested them from the wild ecosystems in which  they live.</p>', 'Loving Earth', 0, 'images2/brands/39.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 17220, 0, 0),
(40, 'Manuka Health Manuka Honey', '<p><strong>Manuka Health Manuka Honey :: </strong>Manuka Health is proud to work with the world''s best natural materials  to bring the highest quality health care products to you. Supported by  the rigours of scientific research, we are confident that Manuka Health  natural health products will enhance your health and well-being.</p>', 'Kadac', 0, 'images2/brands/40.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 16787, 0, 0),
(150, 'Orthoplex :: Orthoplex', '<p><strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Orthoplex Practitioner Only Vitamins are no longer available for sale here. You may like to contact Orthoplex directly or speak to your natural health practitioner for directions to your nearest stockist.&nbsp;</span></strong></p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/150.jpg', '2012-01-18 22:54:28', 15454, 0, 1),
(151, 'Activated Charcoal', '<p>Activated Charcoal may assist to eradicate the body of toxins, chemicals, drugs and wastes to help restore the body to its natural and proper condition.</p>', 'Activated Charcoal', 0, 'images2/brands/151.jpg', '2012-01-19 20:16:00', 4828, 0, 0),
(192, 'Health Food Guys', '<p><strong>The Health Food Guys </strong>is a journey to develop an  Australian natural product range for you. In a world where there never  seems to be enough time to eat healthy, the idea for The Health Food  Guys was born. We wanted to make products without fillers and chemicals  because we believe natural products are more effective and safer than  manufactured products, not found in nature.</p>\n<p id="u4028-5">We are two guys in Melbourne that have always been  into healthy living, and are dedicated to providing healthy and  wholesome products to our customers.</p>\n<p>After 5 years of carefully sourcing and tasting the best ingredients and  all the possible combinations, The Health Food Guys can now offer a  range of products that makes the step towards health and vitality  easier. The option to enjoy what we crave while benefiting from true  nutritional value is now here; thanks to the commitment, research and  expertise offered by The Health Food Guys.</p>', 'Health Food Guys', 0, 'images2/brands/192.jpg', '2013-11-26 00:40:07', 2048, 0, 0),
(186, 'Re Gen Emu Oil', '<div class="span-10 last">\n<div class="common-padding">\n<p>Re Gen Emu Oil :: The emu oil used in <em><strong>REGEN<sup>&reg;</sup></strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong> products is high in essential fatty acids; Omega 3, 6 &amp; 9.</p>\n<p>The use of Emu Oil has increased as more knowledge becomes available   with continued world-wide research confirming the many benefits of this   natural oil as a food capsule. Emu Oil is a good source of essential   fatty acids Omega 3, 6 and 9 that the body requires.</p>\n</div>\n</div>', 'ReGen', 0, 'images2/brands/186.jpg', '2013-07-01 01:15:15', 2350, 0, 0),
(153, 'Argan Oil Issahra :: Moroccan', '<p><strong>Argan Oil Issahra :: Pure &amp; Natural Moroccan Argan Oil</strong></p>\n<p><span style="color: #808000;"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Why Use Argan Oil Skin Care Products?</span></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: x-small;">All our oil products are                      Natural &amp; Organic Argan Oil</span> </li>\n<li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Helps nourish your skin,                      dry hair &amp; nails</span> </span> </li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: x-small;">Helps <span style="text-decoration: underline;">reduce</span> wrinkles                      &amp; Fine Lines</span> </li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: x-small;">Prevents stretch marks</span> </li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: x-small;">Helps Strengthen your hair                      &amp; stimulate re-growth</span> </li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana; font-size: x-small;">Issahra Range contains all                      Natural Ingredients</span> </li>\n</ul>', 'Argan Issahra', 0, 'images2/brands/153.jpg', '2012-02-02 19:04:20', 4069, 0, 0),
(41, 'MiVitality', '<p><strong>MiVitality</strong> :: The world''s first certified organic skin, body, hair, oral and health care. Developed in Australia, MiVitality products are independently certified by Australian Certified Organic (ACO) and the United States Department of Agriculture (USDA) to the highest international food standards.</p>', 'Neil Greenhill', 0, 'images2/brands/41.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3697, 0, 0),
(43, 'Musashi Sports Nutrition', '<p><strong>Musashi Sports Nutrition<br /></strong></p>\n<p>All of Musashi&rsquo;s products are specially designed to assist with the performance needs of athletes from the elite to the everyday level and can assist with muscle development, energy, recovery, figure/toning, and general vitality. Musashi has over 20 years experience in the development of supplements and sports nutrition products.</p>', 'Musashi', 0, 'images2/brands/43.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 4459, 0, 0),
(44, 'Nature''s Goodness', '<p><strong>Nature''s Goodness</strong></p>\n<p>In recent years Dr George Kowalski, who is the creative driving force, and Nature''s Goodness Australia have continued to develop new and innovative natural health products for Australian and overseas markets. These products include Australian Propolis, Goji juice, Resveratrol capsules and Resveratrol Juice, Acai Power juice and Acai Power powder, Cherry Juice, natural toothpastes, natural diabetic products and many more.</p>\n<p>All Nature''s Goodness Australia products are extensively tested for quality and effectiveness.</p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/44.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 4524, 0, 0),
(45, 'Nutralife Vitamins', '<p>Nutra-Life''s team of quality assurance staff operates Nutra-Life''s high tech laboratory and are the key to measuring and improving quality standards. This team administers the rigorous testing carried out on raw materials, blended and finished product. The manufacturing plant is also Halal approved by local Islamic authorities. In addition quality assurance checks are carried out throughout the entire manufacturing process.<br /> In addition, there is strict environmental monitoring of plant and equipment to eliminate chances of contamination.</p>', 'Vitaco', 0, 'images2/brands/45.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 5325, 0, 0),
(93, 'Wotnot Naturals', '<p><strong>WOTNOT Naturals</strong> was started by Sinead Roberts and Sioned Guard after  launching the first environmentally friendly nappy in Australia, Moltex  Oko.  "As our customers grew to love the quality and eco credentials of  the Moltex nappy they asked for complementary products of an equally  high standard and with all natural ingredients.  And so WOTNOT Naturals  was born and continues to grow with the feedback and requests from our  customers".</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/93.jpg', '2010-10-06 17:47:22', 3633, 0, 0),
(47, 'Nutrition Care', '<p>Nutrition Care Pharmaceuticals is committed to providing drug-free, safe and effective health care products to people all over the world. We strive to promote health research and education, disease prevention, and truthful information about medical alternatives. Above all, we seek to empower our customers, health professionals, associates and consumers with the power of nutritional and herbal medicines.</p>', 'Nutrition Care', 0, 'images2/brands/47.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 9229, 0, 0),
(48, 'Oil4Life Coconut Oil', '<p><strong>Oil4Life personnel take pride in:</strong><br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Meeting international organic standards.<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Only sourcing the highest quality organic products that are independently tested and certified to be clean, hygienic, unpolluted and chemical/GE free.<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Frequently meeting with growers and suppliers and nurturing a culture of continual improvement and self assessment.<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Ensuring our partners abide by strict procedures and recognize the benefits of chemically/G.E. free modern science and technology.</p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/48.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 4237, 0, 0),
(49, 'OmegaGen Krill Oil', '<p><strong>OmegaGen Krill Oil</strong></p>\n<p>Unlike fish oils, OmegaGen NKO carries omega-3s in the form of phospholipid liposomes or little packages that helps your body absorb omega-3&rsquo;s. Standard fish oils lack this phospholipid complex, instead containing omega-3 fatty acids in the form of free triglycerides. OmegaGen is also rich in omega-3&rsquo;s, phospholipids and powerful anti-oxidants.</p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/49.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 4504, 0, 0),
(50, 'Pharma Foods', '<p>The Pharma Foods Professional Range has been designed to address the causes of clinical disorders, not just the signs and symptoms.<br /> The core principles of natural medicine are the basis on which our products and programs are formulated.</p>', 'BioCeuticals', 0, 'images2/brands/50.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3951, 0, 0),
(51, 'Power Super Foods', '<p><strong>Power Super Foods</strong> specialize in organic, vegan, raw, Low GI, fairly traded,  gluten-and-dairy-free functional foods, and our drive to lead the  industry in introducing these unique foods to the Australian marketplace  is appreciated by health conscious consumers around the country. Our  premium quality &ldquo;superfoods&rdquo; are always free of artificial preservatives  or colours, free of synthetic flavourings or additives.</p>\n<p>Certified organic means they are grown without the application of  petrochemical fertilizers or chemical pesticides, and are non-GMO and  non-irradiated.</p>', 'IPDC', 0, 'images2/brands/51.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 5529, 0, 0),
(154, 'Pretorius Vitamins Australia', '<p><strong>Pretorius Melatonin 6X :: Homeopathic</strong></p>\n<p>This supplement may help to relieve stress, nervous tension and mild  anxiety.  Pretorius Melatonin Homoeopathic can also help relieve  insomnia when  taken before bedtime and helps provide stamina and  endurance when taken  in the morning. Is useful for establishing sleep  patterns to overcome  jetlag.</p>', 'Pretorius', 0, '', '2012-02-06 22:41:09', 3153, 0, 0),
(52, 'QSilica', '<p><span style="font-size: larger;"><strong>QSilica. Beauty from the inside out.</strong></span></p>\n<p>Qsilica Colloidal Silica is a colloidal suspension of microscopic particles of mineral silica.</p>\n<p>Colloidal silica may be utilised by the body to help strengthen and support healthy connective tissue, skin, hair, nails, bones &amp; teeth.</p>\n<p><span style="font-size: larger;">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Planet Health', 0, 'images2/brands/52.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 4734, 0, 0),
(54, 'Soleo Organics', '<p><strong>Soleo Organics</strong></p>\n<p>Soleo''s highly skilled team of Naturopaths &amp; formulating chemists have spent many years working with natural ingredients &amp; testing formulas to deliver products which <strong>DO NOT</strong> include recognized skin irritants.</p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/54.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3710, 0, 0),
(55, 'Southern Light Herbs', '<p><strong>Southern Light Herbs</strong> :: Over the last 18 years, Southern Light Herbs has worked to promote the growth of organic herb production in Australia. Today, supported by our wonderful network of over 40 dedicated growers, we grow, process and proudly distribute a diverse range of premium Australian quality organic teas, medicinal and culinary herbs to our loyal customers within the health food, wholefood and natural therapies sectors.</p>\n<p><span style="color: red;"><strong style="filter: true;">WESTERN AUSTRALIA RESTRICTIONS apply to any plants or parts of plants, including fruit and seed, brought into Western Australia. Some of the products by Southern Light Herbs are not allowed into Western Australia. Please check with Quarrantine before purchasing.<br /></strong></span></p>', 'Southern Light', 0, 'images2/brands/55.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 5641, 0, 0),
(56, 'Sylk Lubricant', '<p><strong>Sylk Lubricant :: </strong>Improve your sex life naturally, easily and inexpensively with Sylk, our unique natural personal lubricant not only alleviates dryness, it also<br /> <br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Helps put you quickly ''in the mood''<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Enhances sensitivity in women and on men<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Increases sexual pleasure</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/56.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3653, 0, 0),
(57, 'The Original Vegesorb', '<p><strong>The Original Vegesorb </strong>:: Kym Volp, the creator and director of Vegesorb, used her background as a Research Assistant in Biotechnology to specifically design a natural, unfragranced, vegetable based moisturiser that was the culmination of Kym''s academic and scientific expertise and two years product development and client feedback. The focus during development was to utilise vegetable derived ingredients to create an emulsion that would not only boost skin moisture levels but also provide vital skin compatible oils.</p>', 'Nathan Small', 0, 'images2/brands/57.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3789, 0, 0),
(58, 'Thompsons Vitamins', '<p><strong>Thompsons Vitamins</strong> :: Thompson&rsquo;s use of superior quality ingredients, our unique formulations, and the credibility of our clinical data ensure our products deliver enhanced performance and measurable health benefits.</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/58.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 11569, 0, 0),
(59, 'Thursday Plantation', '<p><span style="font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #231f20; line-height: 18px;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;"> </strong></strong></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16pt; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;">:: FANTASTIC PRICES ::</span></strong> </strong><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16pt; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;">&nbsp;</span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline !important; padding: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 16pt; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 24px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px initial initial;">:: WORLDWIDE DELIVERY ::</span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n<p><a class="product-tile-title" href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/125">Buy Tea Tree Oil :: Pure Australian :: First Aid Kit in a Bottle</a></p>\n<p><strong style="font-weight: bold;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;"> </strong></strong></p>\n<p>Thursday Plantation, the original Tea Tree oil company of Australia, produces products based around the purest Tea Tree oil from the delicate flower and leaf tip of Melaleuca alterbfolia. Widely acclaimed as a near perfect anticeptic, Tea tree oil has been put to an amazing spectrum of uses from shampoo, toothpaste and smelly feet to boils, acne and head lice.</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/59.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 49165, 0, 0),
(60, 'Totally Natural Products', '<p>Totally Natural Products pride themselves on creating high quality herbal and nutritional supplements. Using their vast knowledge and experience in digestive health, Totally Natural Products are constantly developing new products that focus on supporting your body&rsquo;s organs that are responsible for cleansing and maintaining the digestive system.</p>\n<p>Established in 1995 Totally Natural Products is a family owned company and is 100% Australian owned.</p>', 'Totally Natural', 0, 'images2/brands/60.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 4008, 0, 0),
(61, 'Trilogy Skincare', '<p><strong>Trilogy Skincare</strong> :: At Trilogy we believe the most powerful ingredients for your skin come from nature. To us beauty is far more than cosmetic - it&rsquo;s about a glowing complexion reflecting truly healthy skin and a balanced approach to life.</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/61.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3993, 0, 0),
(63, 'UV Natural', '<p>UV Natural products are carefully formulated using naturally derived ingredients and zinc oxide to protect from the sun&rsquo;s harmful UVA and UVB rays.</p>\n<p>Light and pure, UV Natural is formulated to also moisturise and soften the skin. UV Natural products are Fragrance and Preservative free.</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/63.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3500, 0, 0),
(64, 'Veromax', '<p>\n	Veromax is a sexual enhancer which has been clinically proved to improve the sexual ability of men &amp; women of all ages and at all levels of sexual capability.<br />\n	<br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '', 0, 'images2/brands/64.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3612, 0, 0),
(65, 'Watersco', '<p><strong>Watersco</strong> :: No manufacturer of water filters has won as many awards for quality or as many high level endorsements &amp; associations as Waters Co. Waters Co have been exporting water filtration products to Australia &amp; the world since 1984</p>', 'Watersco', 0, 'images2/brands/65.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3287, 0, 0),
(95, 'PPC Herbs', '<p>PPC Herbs was built with the plentiful supply of  					clean green organic Australian herbs right here on our  					doorsteps. From the very beginning, PPC Herbs saw that the health  					benefits of natural medicines and therapies were largely  					dependant on the supply of uncontaminated ingredients. So  					far 85% of our products are made with Australian Organic  					Herbs, and we are 100% Australian owned and controlled.</p>', 'Unique', 0, 'images2/brands/95.jpg', '2010-10-06 18:58:02', 3705, 0, 0),
(67, 'WYLD', '<p><strong>WYLD </strong>contains natural herbs along with added vitamins and minerals so that you can look and feel your best without worrying about the harmful side effects.<br /> <br /> As WYLD supports a healthy and balanced lifestyle, we believe in using ingredients that work with the body''s natural processes so that you can get the most out of your life the natural way.</p>', '', 0, 'images2/brands/67.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3595, 0, 0),
(68, 'Zuii Natural Cosmetics', '<p>Zuii Organics&rsquo; timeless and evolving colour palette is created with the benefits of unique organic floral ingredients, essential oils, as well as vitamins and minerals to allow you to create any look you desire whilst nurturing, protecting and improving the skin.</p>\n<p>Not tested on animals, No petrochemicals, No parabens, No talc, No Synthetics, Preservative Free, No GM ingredients is the Zuii commitment to Love of Nature and Organics.</p>', 'Zuii ', 0, 'images2/brands/68.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 5195, 0, 0),
(69, 'Phyto Shield', '<p><strong>Phyto Shield</strong> :: New Zealand is one of the best sources of botanical, agricultural and mineral preparations. Its isolation and natural flora and fauna provides the ideal source of phyto nutrients.<br /> <br /> No animal testing is done on the products, most of the ingredients used are environmentally friendly, and the products are manufactured in a nuclear-free environment.</p>', 'Unique', 0, 'images2/brands/69.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3633, 0, 0),
(70, 'Riddells Creek', '<p>Riddells Creek. Go Organic!<br /> <br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Flouride free * Sulphate free * Vegan Friendly * Mineral oil free<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * BFA Certified Organic * No synthetic chemicals added * Not Genetically Modified<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * Non Toxic * No Additives * No fragrances * No artificial emulsifiers<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; * No artificial preservatives * No animal ingredients * No colours * Not tested on animals.</p>', 'Biologika', 0, 'images2/brands/70.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 3572, 0, 0),
(94, 'Suvana Organic Beauty', '<p>Suvana''s entire range is certified organic, which means all our products are made from Certified Organic and Natural ingredents.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Unique', 0, 'images2/brands/94.jpg', '2010-10-06 18:48:10', 3744, 0, 0),
(71, 'The Jojoba Company', '<h2 style="color: #c098c2;">100% Pure Golden Jojoba</h2>\n<p>Pesticide Free, Easily Absorbed, Natural Australian Jojoba Oil Skincare</p>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.australianvitamins.com/products/view/53" target="_blank">Click here to view the 100% Pure Golden Jojoba Oil<br /></a></p>\n<p><strong style="cursor: pointer; color: #3b5998; padding: 8px 10px 10px; font-family: ''lucida grande'', tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px; display: inline !important;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<div class="_8m ">\n<div class="attachmentText fsm fwn fcg"><a class="pam shareText" rel="nofollow" href="http://www.australianvitamins.com/products/view/2388" target="_blank"> </a></div>\n<a class="pam shareText" rel="nofollow" href="http://www.australianvitamins.com/products/view/2388" target="_blank"> </a></div>', 'Jojoba Company', 0, 'images2/brands/71.jpg', '2010-05-21 01:30:00', 46803, 0, 0),
(72, 'Blackmores Vitamins', '<p><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: 21px; line-height: 24px;"><strong> </strong></span></span></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-weight: normal;"><strong> </strong></span></strong></p>\n<p><strong> <strong> </strong></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="display: inline !important;"><strong><strong>Blackmores Vitamins</strong></strong></p>\n<p><strong><strong> </strong></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="display: inline !important;"><strong><strong><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16.0pt; line-height: 115%;">:: FANTASTIC PRICES ::</span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n<p><strong><strong> </strong></strong><strong><strong> </strong></strong></p>\n<p><strong><strong><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 16.0pt; line-height: 115%;">:: WORLDWIDE DELIVERY ::</span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n<p>Blackmores products are developed by experts, using a combination of scientific evidence and hundreds of years of traditional knowledge. Blackmores products are made to exacting requirements, under the principles of good manufacturing practice and using ingredients sourced from around the world. "Our products are required to meet both our own and governments'' stringent standards of safety, quality and efficacy."</p>', 'Blackmores', 0, 'images2/brands/72.jpg', '2010-06-02 01:30:00', 101733, 0, 0),
(73, 'Fusion Health Vitamins', '<p>Fusion Health vitamin products represent the ancient wisdom of Chinese herbal medicine, transformed by modern scientific methods of extraction and dose delivery. All ingredients are energetically balanced and synergistically combined to provide therapeutic benefits consistent with 3,000 years of recorded tradition.</p>', 'Fusion ', 0, 'images2/brands/73.jpg', '2010-06-02 01:30:00', 10042, 0, 0),
(74, 'InEssence Oils', '<p><strong>InEssence Oils</strong></p>\n<p>In 1986, In Essence began with a selection of pure essential oils for therapeutic use. Today we are recognised not only as Australia''s aromatherapy pioneer and market leader, but also as an expert in the field of naturally-active Anti-Ageing Skincare, botanical Body Care, Therapeutic Remedies and aromatic Home Ambience solutions.</p>', 'InEssence', 0, 'images2/brands/74.jpg', '2010-06-02 01:30:00', 4137, 0, 0),
(75, 'Bosisto''s', '<p>Bosisto''s specializes in pure, natural, Australian Eucalyptus Oil based products with the clean fresh fragrance of the Australian bush.</p>', 'Kadac', 0, 'images2/brands/75.jpg', '2010-06-02 01:30:00', 3707, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `brands` (`id`, `title`, `description`, `supplier`, `feature`, `image_feature`, `timestamp`, `views`, `disabled`, `hidden_price`) VALUES
(76, 'Grahams Natural''s', '<p>Grahams Natural Alternatives was created after my young son, Ryan developed severe eczema at 14 month of age. I also suffered from eczema as a child, but it was very hard to see Ryan in pain as well. Through trial and error our first product Calendulis Plus cream was developed. It has been over 9 years now and we now have a range of unique products that are designed for those with sensitive skin.</p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/76.jpg', '2010-06-02 01:30:00', 4199, 0, 0),
(77, 'Comvita Manuka Honey', '<p><strong>Comvita Manuka Honey</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Quick Links: </strong><span style="font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana;" lang="EN-US"><a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/1573">UMF 5+ Manuka</a> :: <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/1574">UMF 10+ Manuka</a> :: <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/1575">UMF 15+ Manuka</a> :: <a href="http://australianvitamins.com/products/view/1576">UMF 18+ Manuka</a></span></p>\n<p>At Comvita, our number one priority is to provide you with high quality Comvita and effective natural healthcare solutions. We go directly to the source where nature is at its most powerful. By doing this we deliver nature in its most effective state, through unique ingredients that are at the heart of all our products. Our high grade Manuka honey is supplied to us by our beekeepers who meet stringent quality control measures. The Manuka honey used in our Medihoney products is sourced exclusively from our own medical grade beekeeping operation.</p>', 'Comvita', 0, 'images2/brands/77.jpg', '2010-06-02 01:30:00', 8250, 0, 0),
(187, 'Melrose Health', '<p><strong>Melrose Health </strong>:: Our aim is to be Australia''s most trusted and respected whole body health company. Wherever possible we use ingredients from Australian organic farms and our products are developed and manufactured under the rigorous scrutiny of our qualified health professionals.  <br /> <br /> We hold a therapeutic goods processing license, are certified Organic by ACO, the organic certifying arm of the Biological Farmer Association and we ensure no animal tests have been conducted on our products or ingredients.</p>', 'Melrose', 0, 'images2/brands/187.jpg', '2013-08-19 21:12:51', 2043, 0, 0),
(79, 'Author: Bill Statham', '<p>Bill Statham lives with his wife and business partner Kay Lancashire in the picturesque Gippsland region of Victoria. He is a researcher and writer with an interest in health education and a commitment to making a positive difference to the health of people and the environment. Bill studied and practised homeopathy both in Australia and the UK for over ten years.</p>', 'Health Magic', 0, 'images2/brands/79.jpg', '2010-06-02 01:30:00', 3802, 0, 0),
(80, 'Australian Bush Flowers', '<p>Australian Bush Flowers :: Australia has the world''s oldest and highest number of flowering plants exhibiting tremendous beauty and strength. Also Australia is relatively unpolluted and metaphysically has a very wise, old energy.<span class="txtNGreen12"> At this time there is a tremendous new  vitality in this country. This, combined with the inherent power of the  land, is why the Australian Bush Flower Essences are unique.  Practitioners and prescribers world wide are now incorporating the  Australian Essences to form an integral part of their therapy.</span></p>', 'Planet Health', 0, 'images2/brands/80.jpg', '2010-06-02 01:30:00', 20236, 0, 0),
(81, 'S.A. Shark Cartilage', '<p><strong>S.A. Shark Cartilage</strong> :: All South Australian Shark Cartilage products are Ocean Cleaned - an entirely natural process that is unmatched by its level of purity. No sharks are targeted directly for the creation of these products. 100% Australian made and owned.</p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/81.jpg', '2010-06-02 01:30:00', 3794, 0, 0),
(82, 'Novogen', '<p>Novogen, creators of Trinovin, is addressing the urgent area of medical need through the Novogen isoflavonoid technology platform - a platform that the Company believes offers the real prospect of not only treating, but also preventing, the onset of common degenerative conditions.</p>', 'Evelyn Faye', 0, 'images2/brands/82.jpg', '2010-06-02 01:30:00', 3454, 0, 0),
(86, 'NuFerm Nutrition', '<p>NuFerm Nutrition aim to help replenish the &ldquo;friendly&rdquo; intestinal flora for gut bacterial balance, essential for good digestion and a healthy bowel and immune system.</p>\n<p><span lang="EN-AU">Nothing can beat eating high quality wholefoods as the best source of nutrition for our bodies.<span>&nbsp; </span>All  our Wholefood supplements contain not just the active ingredients but a  variety of synergistic nutrients that help in the absorption and  assimilation of these foods.<span>&nbsp; </span></span></p>\n<p>FermPlus does not contain a single manmade vitamin, synthetic mineral, chemical, preservative, filler, binder or extract. Exactly as nature intended - pure and simple.</p>', 'Nu Ferm', 0, 'images2/brands/86.jpg', '2010-07-13 18:01:40', 4949, 0, 0),
(117, 'The Acumat', '<p>The Acumat&reg; has been designed as an all-purpose EVA matting system to maximise warmth, comfort and     lightweight properties for the health, fitness, outdoor and industrial sectors. The final design can be used for any ground based exercise,     sleeping on during outdoor adventures, or to improve workplace health &amp; safety as an anti-fatigue mat.&nbsp;</p>', 'The Acumat', 0, 'images2/brands/117.jpg', '2011-03-01 20:31:56', 3548, 0, 0),
(90, 'Karpati Natural Hair Care', '<p><strong>Karpati Natural Hair Care</strong> :: Each product in this inventive new Karpati Natural Hair Care range has not been tested on animals and contains only the good, natural, nourishing ingredients, which aid in promoting healthy, strong and manageable hair. Ingredients used include: Avocado, Olive, Coconut and Vegetable oil, Vanilla Bean, Chamomile and Green Tea extracts and Vitamins A, B, B12, C and E.</p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/90.jpg', '2010-07-27 18:09:57', 4047, 0, 0),
(139, 'Taiga A320 :: Bioeffective A ', '<p><strong>Bioeffective A 320</strong>, also known  as Conifer Green Needle Complex. A  natural &nbsp;biologically active compound  extracted from green conifer  needles. CGNC contains vitamins, minerals,  fatty and resin acids,  chlorophyll, polyprenols, phytosterols and  carotenoids. It is a potent  antioxidant.</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/139.jpg', '2011-09-08 02:12:53', 4617, 0, 0),
(97, 'Watson & Son Manuka Honey', '<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong>Watson &amp; Son Manuka Honey</strong> is harvested from some of the most  remote and pristine regions of New Zealand from the flowers of our  native Manuka tree. </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">It is a unique taonga (treasure) of our land.  Naturally occurring Methylglyoxal is an ingredient present in genuine  Manuka honey. We guarantee that all our Manuka honey is tested and  verified for its Methylglyoxal content, measured in mg /kg.</span></p>', 'Planet Health', 0, 'images2/brands/97.jpg', '2010-10-07 14:45:08', 5280, 0, 0),
(98, 'Essenzza Health', '<p><strong>Essenzza Health</strong></p>\n<p>Ear Candling has gained much popularity over recent years and the use  of Ear Candles provides an alternative natural approach to tending your  mind and body. Essenzza''s Ear Candle range has been developed with the  customer in mind with a number of leading industry features, such as our  comfort filter, stop ring and protective disk, to ensure your  experience of ear candling is safe and beneficial.</p>\n<p>"Let your ears tell you the difference"</p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/98.jpg', '2010-10-13 12:43:43', 3688, 0, 0),
(113, 'Nutra Organics Superfoods', '<p>Nutra Organics products are scientifically formulated to provide the  wholesome goodness and essential nutrition many of us are missing in our  modern lives.&nbsp; Our formulations provide you with a convenient way to  get the phytonutrients, vitamins, minerals, anti-oxidants, anthocyanins,  alkaline greens and more that your body needs to look and feel healthy,  refreshed and energised.</p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/113.jpg', '2010-12-15 19:58:04', 3792, 0, 0),
(99, 'Synergy Natural', '<p><strong>Synergy Natural Products </strong>is a Sydney, Australia based distributor of Green Superfoods. Synergy Natural Products Pty Ltd was created to provide natural  wholefood health products to the consumer at an affordable price with no  quality compromise. We are an ethical and philosophical company  passionate in our ideals to bring quality and good health to everyone.</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/99.jpg', '2010-10-14 10:42:25', 4535, 0, 0),
