tyle="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;">It has taken over 10 years of research to discover the wonderful properties of the plants we use in our products. Certified organic essential oil has a great therapeutic benefit to skin, body and wellbeing. It is 100% safe and effective to use.</p>', 'Unique', 0, 'images2/brands/100.jpg', '2010-10-21 15:30:07', 4120, 0, 0),
(101, 'Nirvana Health Products', '<p><strong>Nirvana Health Products</strong> have developed and  manufactured superior quality products without the use of synthetic and  harmful additives. Only the most natural, best quality, &ldquo;Non-GMO&rdquo; ingredients are carefully  selected and then products are manufactured to the most highest standards. All our products are attractively  packaged in the highest grade food recycling material available.</p>\n<p>At <strong>Nirvana Health Products</strong> we are helping to promote issues fundamental to people''s well being, sensible diet, detoxification, pure food, pure water, pure environment and exercise. In particular addressing the issue of excess sugar and toxins in our diets.</p>', 'IPDC', 0, '', '2010-10-22 15:11:23', 3848, 0, 0),
(102, 'Wellbeeing Manuka Honey', '<p><strong>Wellbeeing Manuka</strong> specialize in providing some of the highest antibacterial grade of manuka honey.</p>', 'Leatherwood Int.', 0, '', '2010-10-26 11:56:43', 7860, 0, 0),
(103, 'Solutions 4 Health', '<p><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana,geneva;">Solutions 4  Health is a family-run business.&nbsp; We operate from Sydney Australia.&nbsp; We  first became aware of Oil of Wild Oregano and Royal Tea in mid 2006.&nbsp; We  were so impressed after using these products that we wanted them to be  available to all Australians.</span></p>', 'Oborne', 0, 'images2/brands/103.jpg', '2010-11-02 18:57:43', 3843, 0, 0),
(104, 'ICL Health', '<p>ICL Health provides a range of speciality supplements for supporting everyday good health and preventing disease. Trace Nutrients is a unique line of practitioner-recommended vitamin and  mineral supplements at the forefront of nutritional medicine  preparations. These formulations offer a more precise and  patient-specific approach to nutritional therapy.</p>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/104.jpg', '2010-11-02 19:46:37', 3857, 0, 0),
(105, 'Endura Sports', '<p><strong>Endura Sports</strong></p>\n<p>Endura Sports Nutrition is made and distributed by Health World  Limited. Health World, Australia&rsquo;s leading Natural Health Science  Company, manufacture and distribute quality Natural Medicine.</p>', 'Health World', 0, 'images2/brands/105.jpg', '2010-11-02 21:20:13', 3814, 0, 0),
(106, 'Lucas Papaw Remedies', '<p><strong>Lucas Papaw Remedies</strong></p>\n<p>Our commitment to quality also extends to our selection  of the raw materials used in Lucas Papaw Ointment which are  pharmaceutical grade ingredients.</p>\n<ul>\n<li> Is the same formula developed by Dr T. P. Lucas, unchanged in over 100 years</li>\n<li>The papaya used in Lucas Papaw Ointment is Queensland grown fresh fruit</li>\n<li>Uses fruit that we ferment ourselves</li>\n<li>Lucas Papaw Ointment does not contain polyplasdone, polyvinylpyrrolidone, talc, shellac, sodium laurel sulphate</li>\n<li>Lucas Papaw Ointment is microbiologically tested before it is released</li>\n</ul>', 'Integria', 0, 'images2/brands/106.jpg', '2010-11-04 19:27:50', 4143, 0, 0),
(107, 'Simmons Paw Paw', '<p>Simmons Paw Paw products <strong>use no petrochemicals</strong>.  They simply contain  			the best natural ingredients.</p>', 'unavailable', 0, '', '2010-11-04 19:43:21', 3735, 0, 0),
(108, 'Pure Nutraceuticals', '<p>Pure Nutraceuticals formulates Paw Paw Ointment with Calendula to soothe, moisturise and protect your skin.</p>', 'Oborne', 0, '', '2010-11-04 21:36:58', 3697, 0, 0),
(110, 'Advance Health', '<p><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">Advance Health only use the very best quality naturally fermented CoQ10 available,  which is yeast derived and is produced by Kaneka Corporation. Kaneka Q10  has an all-trans configuration and is bioidentical to your own bodies  Co Q10 and also contains the essential negative electrical charge.</span></p>', 'Advance Health', 0, 'images2/brands/110.jpg', '2010-11-08 18:05:05', 3978, 0, 0),
(111, 'Monzter Labz', '<p><strong>Monzter Labz</strong> <strong>TestOrod </strong></p>\n<p>Whether you&rsquo;re in the gym, on the sports field or in the bedroom,  maintaining normal testosterone levels in your body is important for  performance. So if you want to build big strong muscles, increase your  energy levels, improve your stamina and sex life, Monzter Labz TestOrod  may be just what you need.</p>', 'Totaly Natural ', 0, 'images2/brands/111.jpg', '2010-11-19 01:08:59', 3813, 0, 0),
